says, "Teachers are the worst." I say, "I

01:15:48.079 --> 01:15:53.920
know." We really are. So, we need to

01:15:51.319 --> 01:15:56.279
have people working together all

01:15:53.920 --> 01:16:00.880
year. Bring those teachers into our school
system. I found the 1996

01:15:59.039 --> 01:16:04.039
version of how to do it. I had to dig it

01:16:00.880 --> 01:16:06.640
up. I really did. So, that is what I want
to say. I

01:16:04.039 --> 01:16:09.720
love teaching. I

01:16:06.640 --> 01:16:12.880
love my colleagues, and I think now it is
time to

01:16:09.720 --> 01:16:16.360
