01:23:36.039 --> 01:23:42.840
Stability in teaching, caring, and loving.

01:23:41.119 --> 01:23:47.181
Each of your comments was impressive and
inspiring.

01:23:45.159 --> 01:23:47.199
I was part of you for a long time, and I
love you all.

