01:51:03.960 --> 01:51:09.400
um to respectfully ask the district to
think again about reducing FR's

01:51:07.840 --> 01:51:12.839
kindergarten from five sections down to
four, or at least to pause this

01:51:11.239 --> 01:51:15.360
