I want to thank both of

02:14:18.960 --> 02:14:25.840
them for starting this project, especially
Keith Lezama for

02:14:23.800 --> 02:14:29.360
getting an advisor for each school. This
is something principals

02:14:28.079 --> 02:14:33.479
requested. People were sharing schools,
and

02:14:32.039 --> 02:14:36.319
this made them make tough choices.

02:14:36.520 --> 02:14:41.159
One school had a big problem, and another
school had an Individualized Education Plan

02:14:40.119 --> 02:14:46.279
that needed a lot of help. Which school
should I go to

02:14:43.199 --> 02:14:46.279
if both need attention?

02:14:46.880 --> 02:14:53.600
They couldn't do it. It has really

02:14:51.399 --> 02:14:55.319
helped a lot to have an advisor in every
school.

02:14:53.600 --> 02:14:58.719
I want to mention the picture there. Um

02:14:57.039 --> 02:15:02.800
Joanne Sylva Enjoku could not come
tonight. She is dealing with some

02:15:01.000 --> 02:15:05.760
personal and family matters.

02:15:02.800 --> 02:15:07.400
She is often called the origami lady.

02:15:05.760 --> 02:15:11.679
She does that to help kids open up and
also helps with

02:15:09.760 --> 02:15:14.400
fine motor skills and cultural learning.

02:15:12.680 --> 02:15:18.599
Joanne was one of the people honored
