03:37:58.079 --> 03:38:02.680
to understand who needs help,

03:38:00.399 --> 03:38:05.159
to build trust, and to make a classroom

03:38:02.680 --> 03:38:08.200
where children feel safe to try,

03:38:05.159 --> 03:38:12.159
to speak, to make mistakes, and to grow.

03:38:08.200 --> 03:38:14.280
That does not happen by chance. It happens
