03:39:13.680 --> 03:39:20.680
school is strong, supportive, and
positive.

03:39:18.559 --> 03:39:23.119
I know the district has tough choices to
make,

03:39:20.680 --> 03:39:26.040
but I trust the creativity and

03:39:23.120 --> 03:39:29.240
leadership of the administration to find

03:39:26.040 --> 03:39:31.040
supportive, and positive as it can be.

03:39:29.239 --> 03:39:35.040
I understand that the district has
difficult choices to make,

03:39:33.280 --> 03:39:37.600
but I trust the creativity and the

03:39:35.040 --> 03:39:40.640
leadership of the administration to find

03:39:37.600 --> 03:39:42.200
we discuss other solutions if we need to
make cuts, not

03:39:40.639 --> 03:39:47.520
by taking resources away from our youngest
learners at the start

03:39:44.680 --> 03:39:49.280
of their school journey.

03:39:47.520 --> 03:39:54.159
